   162â†’	PE index.PostingsEncoder
   163â†’
   164â†’	// PD specifies the postings decoder factory to return different postings decoder based on BlockMeta. It is called when opening a block or opening the index file.
   165â†’	// If it is nil then a default decoder is used, compatible with Prometheus v2.
